## 🚀 Installation

### Prerequisites

- **Python**: 3.8 or higher
- **OS**: Windows 10/11, macOS 10.14+, Linux
- **RAM**: 2GB minimum (4GB recommended)
- **Storage**: 100MB for installation

### Step 1: Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/text-summarization-suite.git
cd text-summarization-suite
```

### Step 2: Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### Step 3: Run the Application

```bash
python professional_summarizer.py
```

### Required Dependencies

```txt
tkinter (built-in with Python)
deep-translator>=1.11.0
gTTS>=2.3.0
playsound>=1.3.0
python-docx>=0.8.11
PyPDF2>=3.0.0
sumy>=0.11.0
nltk>=3.8.0
```

### First-Time Setup

The application will automatically download required NLTK data on first run:
- punkt tokenizer
- stopwords corpus

