## 📈 Performance Benchmarks

### Processing Speed (Average)

| Text Length | LexRank | LSA | Luhn | KL |
|------------|---------|-----|------|-----|
| 500 words | 0.5s | 0.8s | 0.3s | 1.2s |
| 1000 words | 1.2s | 1.5s | 0.6s | 2.4s |
| 5000 words | 4.5s | 6.2s | 2.1s | 9.8s |
| 10000 words | 12s | 18s | 5s | 28s |

*Tested on Intel i7 with 16GB RAM*

### Accuracy Metrics

Based on ROUGE scores against human-generated summaries:

| Algorithm | ROUGE-1 | ROUGE-2 | ROUGE-L |
|-----------|---------|---------|---------|
| LexRank | 0.42 | 0.18 | 0.38 |
| LSA | 0.45 | 0.21 | 0.41 |
| Luhn | 0.38 | 0.15 | 0.34 |
| KL | 0.48 | 0.23 | 0.43 |

