## 🛠️ Advanced Configuration

### Custom Settings

Edit `settings.json`:

```json
{
  "sentence_count": "5",
  "summary_style": "⚖️ Balanced",
  "default_language": "English",
  "auto_save_history": true,
  "max_history_items": 100,
  "enable_audio": true,
  "theme": "light"
}
```

### Command Line Options

```bash
# Run with custom settings
python professional_summarizer.py --config custom_settings.json

# Disable audio features
python professional_summarizer.py --no-audio

# Set log level
python professional_summarizer.py --log-level DEBUG
```

