## 🐛 Known Issues

- **PDF Extraction**: Some scanned PDFs may not extract text properly (use OCR first)
- **Audio Playback**: May experience delays on first play (loading gTTS)
- **Large Files**: Documents over 50MB may cause memory issues
- **Translation**: Requires internet connection and may be rate-limited

