## 💡 Tips & Best Practices

1. **For Best Results**:
   - Use texts with at least 500 words
   - Remove headers/footers before processing
   - Check for OCR errors in scanned documents

2. **Performance Optimization**:
   - Close other memory-intensive applications
   - Process one large document at a time
   - Clear cache regularly

3. **Algorithm Selection**:
   - Try multiple methods for comparison
   - Use Compare All for uncertain cases
   - Save good results to Favorites

